562
00:49:52.781 --> 00:49:54.199
Shit.

563
00:49:54.200 --> 00:49:56.402
(CHUCKLES) You got her.

564
00:50:05.628 --> 00:50:08.001
(THUNDER RUMBLING)

565
00:51:06.647 --> 00:51:08.849
